cos(radians(41.31588575)) * cos(radians(latitude)) *
cos(radians(longitude) - radians(19.900912164461147)) +
sin(radians(41.31588575)) * sin(radians(latitude))

) AS distance from `hotels` having `distance` <= 10 order by `distance` asc
